Common.Strapline.Common.Text: LIVE/WORK IN THIS ATTRACTIVE SELF-CONTAINED SUITE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Hotels are delighted to be appointed in offering for sale the 'Freehold Going Concern' interest in the Crown Hotel.

Key investment considerations include:

- Corner allotment on busy Crown and Cleveland Streets

- Expansive four level hotel with bars, function space, rooftop residence and eight recently renovated boutique accommodation rooms

- 24 hour liquor licence, 3 hour gaming shutdown and 30 gaming machines

- 12 month YOY gaming growth up 30%*

- $2.9m* revenue (Jul - Dec 2016) with $990,730* average gaming turnover per week (Jul - Dec 2016)

- Situated outside Sydney lock-out zone, close to new Surry Hills light rail station and Moore Park Entertainment precinct

- Opposite Surry Hills Shopping Centre and proposed Toga major residential development

* approx

Located in one of Sydney’s trendiest suburbs, 202-210 Elizabeth Street offers a unique opportunity to capitalise on a well-placed development on the border of Sydney’s CBD. The site comprises DA approval for a six level mixed use development accommodating ground floor retail and self-contained residential accommodation.

The property represents a top tier development opportunity offering the following key attributes:

- DA approval for 38 self-contained boarding house rooms includinge private bathrooms and kitchens and two exposed ground floor retail shops fronting Elizabeth Street
- 329sqm^ site area
- Extremely close proximity to Sydney CBD, Central Station, transport, retail shopping, recreational parkland and several of the country’s most prestigious universities
- Ideal housing for the area’s thriving demographic of international students, young professionals and key workers
- Favourable B4 – Mixed use zoning

The property will be offered for sale via Public Auction on Tuesday, 15 August 2017 at 10:30am at AuctionWORKS.

^Approximate

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Ideal for owner occupiers and investors

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 1-5 Flinders Street, Surry Hills, a landmark building in the heart of one of Sydney’s most renowned locations, Taylor Square.

Commanding an unrivaled exposure to Taylor Square, the recognisable freehold building is a rare offering in a coveted and tightly held city fringe location.

1-5 Flinders Street, Surry Hills benefits from the following key attributes:
- Landmark Sydney building
- Prime Taylor Square location in the heart of Oxford Street
- Internal area of 922.79sqm*
- Vacant possession property ready for incoming tenant refurbishment
- Island site frontages to Bourke Street, Flinders Street, Patterson Lane and the pedestrian traffic of Taylor Square
- B2 Local Centre zoning allowing for a variety of permissible uses

The property will be offered for sale via Expression of Interest closing on Wednesday 25 October at 4:00pm

*approximate
